('NYTBS-1', 'The Hate U Give', 'Angie Thomas', 399, 239, 40, 10, 'Walker', '2018', 'The New York Times Best Sellers', 'An eye-catching new cover look that is perfect to bring the No. 1 New York Times bestseller, recipient of many awards and much acclaim in the children\'s book world, to a wider crossover audience.\r\n#1 New York Times bestseller\r\nSoon to be a major motion picture, starring Amandla Stenberg\r\n“A classic in the making. ” the Times\r\n“Passionate and uncompromising. ” the Observer\r\n“A masterpiece. ” Huffington Post\r\nStarr Carter\'s world is shattered when she is the only witness to the fatal shooting of her unarmed best friend, Khalil, by a police officer. Now what Starr says could destroy her community. It could also get her killed.\r\nInspired by the Black Lives Matter movement, the multi-award-winning the Hate U Give is a powerful and gripping novel about one\r\ngirl\'s struggle for justice.', 'English', 448);
